-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

How to install P.A.T.H.

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

---:[ Requirements

Libpcap [ http://www.tcpdump.org ]
Perl interpreter
If you want to you the GUI versions you need to install Tk and XFree86 (Xlibs)!

NOTE: If you install the binary versions you also need to install the devel
packages!

---:[ Installation

perl Makefile.PL
make
su
make install clean
This will install the P.A.T.H. modules and scripts.
If your system lacks a required modules make will interrupt and give you
an installation hint.
If you have any problems installing the P.A.T.H. project please have a
look at the FAQ!

